  %h2 Welcome to Sens-it-iv!
  What to expect:
  %ul
    %li
      = link_to "Internal Website:", :controller => 'website', :action => 'index'
      Documents for Sens-it-iv members (Administrator:
      = mail_to "sens-it-iv@planet.nl", "A. Thorbecke"
      )
    /
      <li><a href="https://sens-it-iv-internal.org/phpbb">Forum</a>: For the discussion of Sens-it-iv topics (Administrator: <a href='mailto:sens-it-iv@planet.nl'>A. Thorbecke</a>) </li>
