    %li
      = link_to "Experiments:", :controller => 'experiments', :action => 'index'
      Browse and search experimental data.
    %li
      = link_to "Compounds:", :controller => 'compounds', :action => 'index'
      Information about chemicals for the Sens-it-iv project.
      %ul
        %li
          = link_to "Skin Sensitisation Database", :controller => 'compounds', :action => 'list' , :show => 'all'
          with 211 compounds
        %li
          = link_to "Training Compounds", :controller => 'compounds', :action => 'list', :show => 'training_set'
          Information about reference compounds (e.g. biological activities, solubility, toxicity)
    %li
      = link_to "Data submission:", :controller => :file_upload
      Submit WP8 results

  Please use the 
  = link_to 'Help', :controller => :help
  button for further instructions and if you have problems with this website. If you cannot find a solution you can contact
  = mail_to "sens-it-iv@planet.nl", "A. Thorbecke"
  for the internal website and
  = mail_to "helma@in-silico.de", "C. Helma"
  for the internal database.
  
